[gd_scene load_steps=140 format=3]

; MOUNTAIN — Climb the Peak. Full-scope vertical level.
; Tiers: forested base (spring, cave, waterfall grotto) / mid-tier lodge plateau (rope bridge chasm) /
;   spiral cone + wall-kick gate + observation deck / wind ridge / summit altar.
; Architecture: CSG-carved cave/tunnel system, waterfall cliff with secret grotto,
;   multi-room lodge with window cutouts + chimney, spiral ramp ~3 revolutions.
; Skylift: two towers + cable + cable car box.
; Slide exit: curved very_slippery trough summit -> base.
; Content: 45 yellow coins, 8 red coins, 3 stars (summit, shrine, grotto), 4 1-ups, 1 wing cap.
; Enemies: 8 goomba, 5 koopa, 3 bobomb, 4 cuttlefish, 2 bobomb buddy.
; Spawn: Vector3(0, 1, 30) facing mountain (-Z).

